content:
A U.S. Navy hospital ship arrived in New York harbor on Monday to help relieve local hospitals being overwhelmed by coronavirus patients.
The USNS Comfort will treat non-coronavirus patients, freeing up beds so local hospitals can focus on COVID-19.
